# Registers the ADR-002 §2 production-profile guardrail as a SpringApplication
# listener so it fires BEFORE context/bean binding. If the prod profile is
# active and the configured OIDC issuer is a dev IdP (localhost,
# mock-oauth2-server, loopback), startup aborts.
org.springframework.context.ApplicationListener=\
com.medcore.platform.config.ProdProfileOidcGuard
